Description
This PR adds Multi-Factor Authentication (TOTP) to Continuum Monitor as part of Week 2 of the 14-week enterprise release plan.

What's new:

TOTP support with Google Authenticator, Authy, and Microsoft Authenticator

Backup codes for account recovery

Trusted device option (30 days)

Full audit logging of MFA events

MFA status endpoint (/mfa/status), setup (/mfa/setup), and verify (/mfa/verify)

MFA badge and banner on the marketing page

Also includes:

Code hardening improvements (tested on test droplet):

Systemd units for logs + AI services

Input validation on /api/logs and /api/feedback

Header‑based API key authentication (X-API-Key)

Updated README with MFA and 14‑week plan (removed weekly table for suspense)

